dct_description_sm: Includes text. Sheets 105-106, 108, and 110-112 of Newark, N.J., vol. 1, series; sheets 105-106, 108, and 111-112: New sheet, Sept.. 1918; sheet 110: Add'l sheet, Sept. 1918. Sheets 111-112 show Port Newark.
